From the Infowars web site ::

Alex talks with British columnist and novelist James Delingpole about Al Gore, the Club of Rome, the Georgia Guidestones, Maurice Strong, the New World Order and other topics covered in his latest book, Watermelons. 

Alex also talks with film-maker, former equities broker, and television show host Max Keiser about a "rogue trader" with Switzerland's UBS that lost $2 billion.
